  %h1.sectitle
    What is it<span class="redtext">?</span>

  .what.accordion
    .row
      .realvid
        %iframe{:allowFullScreen => "", :frameborder => "0", :height => "338", :mozallowfullscreen => "", :src => "http://player.vimeo.com/video/29633009", :webkitAllowFullScreen => "", :width => "600"}

    .row
      .one_whole
        %p
          We think relatively simple tools can help us all improve the quality of information on the Internet, and by extension in the greater world around us.
        %p
          Hypothes.is will be a distributed, open-source platform for the collaborative evaluation of information. It will enable sentence-level critique of written words combined with a sophisticated yet easy-to-use model of community peer-review. It will work as an overlay on top of any stable content, including news, blogs, scientific articles, books, terms of service, ballot initiatives, legislation and regulations, software code and more-without requiring participation of the underlying site.
        %p
          It is based on a new draft standard for annotating digital documents currently being developed by the
          = succeed "," do
            %a{:href => "http://openannotation.org"} Open Annotation Collaboration
          a consortium that includes the Internet Archive, NISO (National Information Standards Organization), O'Reilly Books, Amazon, Barnes and Noble, and a number of academic institutions.

        %p
          Interested in participating?
          %a#us_re.tipper Reserve your username.
        %form#register_form.two_thirds.us_re.tip
          #availability_status
          %label{:for => "username", :style => "display: none;"} Choose a Username.
          %input#username.clearFocus{:name => "username", :type => "text", :placeholder => "Choose a Username"}
          %label{:for => "email", :style => "display: none;"} Enter your email.
          %input#email{:name => "email", :type => "text", :placeholder => "Enter your email."}
          %label{:for => "email2", :style => "display: none;"} Confirm your email.
          %input#email2{:name => "email2", :type => "text", :placeholder => "Confirm your email."}
          %input.button{:name => "button", :type => "submit", :value => "Save my username"}

        %div
          And please consider
          %a{:href => "#donate"} donating
          to help us get started!
